OOC: My rabbit died last night so I'm going to make a new Maximal in 
his honor. By the way I would do this in polls but no one's answering 
mine anymore and I want comments about your opinions. Would you be 
willing to have a char in a faction made entirely of proto-humans 
trying to banish the "demons" from their planets, and should they be 
allowed to use magic and energon spear and hammerheads to even the 
odds. If I get 3 supporting replies and no negative ones I'll do it 
(forget it Nemisis you don't count).

A shuttle is crashing to earth.  It lands in North America. It scans a 
small, black and white rabbit. A bot of 80 stellar cycles steps out 
(he was 8).

Old Bot: I look almost as cute as I did when I was 20. Just in a 
different way. From now on everyone can call me Cutie just like the 
ladies did.  BEAST MODE!

He happily hops away.

OOC: Does anyone know how I can make my dialogue less sketchy (shut up 
Nemisis)?
